title: Ophiusa parcemacula
text:
Ophiusa parcemacula is a <a href="moth">moth</a> of the family <a href="Erebidae">Erebidae</a>. It is found in <a href="New%20Guinea">New Guinea</a>, <a href="New%20Caledonia">New Caledonia</a> and the northern half of <a href="Australia">Australia</a>.
The <a href="wingspan">wingspan</a> is about 60 mm.
The larvae feed on "<a href="Loranthaceae">Loranthaceae</a>" and "<a href="Melaleuca%20quinquenervia">Melaleuca quinquenervia</a>".
